    "MissionTokens": {
        "Contractor|BountyDescription": [
            "Got issued another bounty that we could use you on. This one's for <EM4>[TargetName]</EM4>. I don't expect them to go down easy, but that shouldn't be a problem for you. They're last know location was at <EM4>[Location|Address]</EM4>.\n\nSee that you get it done,\n\nBraden Corchado\nLogistics Officer - Stanton Branch\nNorthrock Service Group",
            "Your services are needed once again. This time to track and bring down the notorious <EM4>[TargetName]</EM4>. They were last seen at <EM4>[Location|Address]</EM4>. \n\nDo me a favor and keep it as clean as you can, okay? Might be extra eyes on this one.\n\nThanks for handling this,\n\nBraden Corchado\nLogistics Officer - Stanton Branch\nNorthrock Service Group",
            "Have a bounty for you. <EM4>[TargetName]</EM4>. Not the most high-profile collar, but a nasty piece of work nonetheless. Be good for everyone in the system to have this settled. Their last known location was at <EM4>[Location|Address]</EM4>.\n\nGood luck on the hunt,\n\nBraden Corchado\nLogistics Officer - Stanton Branch\nNorthrock Service Group"
        ],
        "Contractor": [
            "Northrock Service Group"
        ]
    },
